items.name: Minecraft-IP-Range-Sweeper
items.description: Multi-threaded scanner generator written in Python, designed to detect potential Minecraft servers on a specified port (default: 25565) by sweeping across customizable ranges of Class C subnets within a fixed base IP block. This tool helps your friends find your private Minecraft server when the public IP changes based on your rough IP ranges.
